text:
Hey all, I hope all is well. I recently inherited a HS instance that includes around 30 custom email modules but none of them are mobile responsive. For example I have a 3 column module that I would like to stack. I have attached a preview of the module and the code is below. Can someone help me please. Thank you :pray::skin-tone-2:

Update: I have since managed to get the columns to stack, however unable to make then width:100% in mobile without affecting the desktop layout

```{% if module.section_on_off %}

    &lt;table class="_columnContentTable" role="presentation" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" align="center" width="auto" bgcolor="{{ module.section_background.color }}"&gt;

      &lt;tbody bgcolor="{{ module.section_background.color }}"&gt;
        &lt;tr bgcolor="{{ module.section_background.color }}"&gt;
          &lt;td width="100%"  colspan="3"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/td&gt;
        &lt;/tr&gt;

        &lt;tr bgcolor="{{ module.section_background.color }}"&gt;
           &lt;td width="15" bgcolor="{{ module.section_background.color }}"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/td&gt;
           &lt;td width="570" bgcolor="{{ module.section_background.color }}"&gt;
              &lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%" class="_columnContentTable" gcolor="{{ module.section_background.color }}"&gt;
                &lt;tbody bgcolor="{{ module.section_background.color }}"&gt;
                  &lt;tr bgcolor="{{ module.section_background.color }}"&gt;
                    &lt;td colspan="3" class="column_columnContent" bgcolor="{{ module.section_background.color }}" align="center" height="100%" valign="top" width="100%" style="padding: 10px 0;" bgcolor="{{ module.section_background.color }}"&gt;
                        {{ module.section_heading }}
                    &lt;/td&gt;
                  &lt;/tr&gt;
                  &lt;tr&gt;
          {% for item in module.add_column_here %}
          &lt;td class="column_columnContent" bgcolor="{{ module.section_background.color }}" width="180px" style="box-sizing: border-box;padding-left:15px; padding-right:15px;padding-top:10px; padding-bottom: 18px; display:inline-block; vertical-align:middle;" align="center" valign="top"&gt;
            &lt;div&gt;
              {{ item.title_text }}
            &lt;/div&gt;
            &lt;div&gt;
              &lt;div&gt;
                &amp;nbsp;
              &lt;/div&gt;
              {% if item.icon.src %}
                {% set sizeAttrs = 'width="{{ item.icon.width }}" height="{{ item.icon.height }}"' %}
                {% if item.icon.size_type == 'auto' %}
                  {% set sizeAttrs = 'style="max-width: 100%; height: 100;"' %}
                {% elif item.icon.size_type == 'auto_custom_max' %}
                  {% set sizeAttrs = 'width="{{ item.icon.max_width }}" height="{{ item.icon.max_height }}" style="max-width: 100%; height: auto;"' %}
                {% endif %}
                 {% set loadingAttr = item.icon.loading != 'disabled' ? 'loading="{{ item.icon.loading }}"' : '' %}
                &lt;img src="{{ item.icon.src }}" alt="{{ item.icon.alt }}" {{ loadingAttr }} {{ sizeAttrs }}  width="{{ item.icon.width }}" height="auto" width="160" style="height:auto;"&gt;
              {% endif %}

            &lt;/div&gt;
          &lt;/td&gt;
          {% endfor %}
                  &lt;/tr&gt;
                &lt;/tbody&gt;
              &lt;/table&gt;
           &lt;/td&gt;
        &lt;/tr&gt;
        &lt;tr bgcolor="{{ module.section_background.color }}"&gt;
          &lt;td bgcolor="{{ module.section_background.color }}" width="100%"  colspan="3"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/td&gt;
        &lt;/tr&gt;
      &lt;/tbody&gt;
    &lt;/table&gt;
{% endif %}```
